          <li style="margin-bottom:var(--space-2);">Revoke Google access at any time via your Google account settings</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To request account deletion, please contact us at <span style="color:var(--gold);">habari@hisazangu.co.tz</span>.</p>

        <h5 style="color:var(--text-primary);margin-top:var(--space-6);margin-bottom:var(--space-3);">8. Changes to This Policy</h5>
